         VERSION=1.2.5
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:12520d47d664ea49df99c5884e6bff86cc5919af2038f8a9b6333bcac3ee00ee8d1da664bed16aff7f2f3df560ebee196b4cd7f4884694b0f4dfa2df4dc1e6d2
